2026-04-30T13:03:42.3016146Z               "id": "4fcde8b57b801cac65ca60cb503f470c5d485780",
2026-04-30T13:03:42.3020072Z               "message": "UI polish: domain history, wrap, consistent nav, delete revoked\n\n- Persist recently validated domains in localStorage and back the\n  domain input with a <datalist> for native autocomplete\n- Allow the default DKIM selectors textarea (and other text textareas)\n  on the config screen to wrap, while preserving pre-formatting for the\n  raw JSON view\n- Unify the top nav across the validator, tokens, and config pages:\n  same Validator | Tokens | Config | who | Sign out layout, with the\n  current page marked as the active item; sign-out hides when auth\n  is disabled\n- Allow the root user to permanently delete revoked users (cascading\n  through revoked descendants). Adds AuthService.Delete, surfaces an\n  isRoot flag on /api/auth/me and /api/auth/users, exposes\n  DELETE /api/auth/users/{username}, and shows a Delete button only to\n  root on revoked rows in the tokens UI",
2026-04-30T13:03:42.3051797Z               "timestamp": "2026-04-30T12:41:17Z",
2026-04-30T13:03:42.3052438Z               "tree_id": "db4c5e01d4840961766bc6c19a5100034f983952",
