2026-04-30T13:03:42.3057593Z               "id": "7a0158ec813949f5af8236506772907579e06ec4",
2026-04-30T13:03:42.3058495Z               "message": "Hide Tokens nav link from non-admins\n\nNon-admin users cannot issue or view tokens, so the menu item should\nnot be shown to them. The link is now revealed only when /api/auth/me\nreports the caller is an admin (or auth is disabled).",
